Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.45,0:00:13.87,Italics,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Countryside tap water is delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.87,0:00:15.14,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,Nukumizu-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.06,0:00:17.43,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.43,0:00:19.13,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,I got a little thirsty.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.63,0:00:20.98,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,What are {\i1}you{\i0} doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.32,0:00:25.02,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,I can't keep my eyes shut.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.03,0:02:02.79,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Did Yakishio already go to bed?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.25,0:02:06.08,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,She just told me she was going out for a run.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.46,0:02:07.48,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,At this hour?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.57,0:02:12.48,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Did you talk to Yakishio \Nabout what happened before?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.97,0:02:16.43,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,I'm worried I might say the wrong thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.88,0:02:18.67,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,The wrong thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.28,0:02:23.72,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I can really root\N for anyone this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.27,0:02:28.23,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,I can understand why Asagumo-san is \Nnervous since they just started dating.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.56,0:02:31.66,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,But she should just talk \Nto her boyfriend directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.66,0:02:35.92,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think she should be testing \Ntheir relationship in such sneaky ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.35,0:02:37.38,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,At all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.92,0:02:43.18,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he's partly responsible, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.18,0:02:44.14,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.14,0:02:49.34,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I mean, it's clear to me \Nthat Ayano isn't a bad guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.34,0:02:52.45,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,But I can understand why \NAsagumo-san would be nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.39,0:02:55.50,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,But Asagumo-san is—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.50,0:02:56.40,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,You know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.45,0:02:59.27,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Let's stop talking about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.12,0:03:07.18,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I mean, I don't want you saying bad \Nthings about people behind their back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.50,0:03:09.95,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. That was a weird thing to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.22,0:03:15.52,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,Fine. Then this is the last thing I'll say.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.52,0:03:20.59,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,If Lemon-chan's so bad at hiding her feelings\Nthat she accidentally blurts them out,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.59,0:03:23.72,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,she should've just told him a year ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.72,0:03:25.25,Italics,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,That's rich, coming from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.84,0:03:31.02,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,Asagumo-san and Ayano-kun, too. \NThe three of them are a complete mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.47,0:03:35.90,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,There. It's out of my system. From here on,\N it's back to "good girl Yanami-chan."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.84,0:03:39.01,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,But you know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.00,0:03:46.83,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,Lemon-chan's my friend, so if I was talking \Nto her now, I'd probably tell her this:
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.85,0:03:50.07,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,"You should go out with him."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.62,0:03:51.33,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.34,0:03:57.80,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,She should steal him. \NAsagumo-san said she'd step aside, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.48,0:04:01.01,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,But that'd be really—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.01,0:04:03.89,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,Lemon-chan wouldn't want that, would she?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.24,0:04:08.61,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like it very much, \Nbut even I can see she's right about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.43,0:04:15.36,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'll go for a walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.07,0:04:17.40,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,At this hour?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.72,0:04:20.08,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,The moon looks really pretty tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.00,0:04:26.40,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,If you go back down the road \Nwe came up, there's a shrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.82,0:04:30.99,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,Lemon-chan says that's where \Nshe goes when she needs to think.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.39,0:04:34.63,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to look for Yakishio, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.63,0:04:37.92,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm? Then maybe I'll go look for her instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.20,0:04:43.26,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,Think I should turn Lemon-chan \Ninto a bad girl like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.45,0:04:47.62,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.72,0:05:11.42,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,You know, I really didn't \Nintend to get in their way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.29,0:05:18.04,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if I'll be able to stay friends \Nwith Mitsuki after this. Maybe not.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.50,0:05:23.99,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Now that he knows how you feel, \Nthings probably won't be the same anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.82,0:05:25.97,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,That Mitsuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.51,0:05:30.38,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,I think he's having trouble setting \Nboundaries with Asagumo-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.38,0:05:36.13,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,Like deciding how to react to her advances. \NOr how to deepen their relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.49,0:05:40.20,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, okay, but relationship advice aside,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.83,0:05:43.15,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,I bet you don't want to hear about all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.15,0:05:45.64,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I'm not a kid, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.64,0:05:50.16,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,Those two are going out. \NThese things happen sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.96,0:05:56.07,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,If you try to stay friends with him \Nlike before, this will keep happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.76,0:05:58.07,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.23,0:06:03.67,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,I know. That's why I was trying \Nto give Mitsuki advice as a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.15,0:06:07.60,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,I thought if I did that, I could accept\N the reality of how things were.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.98,0:06:10.09,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,I really thought I could accept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.80,0:06:11.73,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,But you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.33,0:06:18.21,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,I still couldn't help wishing\N he was attracted to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.51,0:06:23.50,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,At first, I sincerely just wanted\N to give Mitsuki advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.17,0:06:29.04,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,But then, every time I was going \Nto meet him, I'd get so excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.61,0:06:33.59,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,I started thinking that I wanted \Nthings to stay like that forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.08,0:06:36.55,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,And then... And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.40,0:06:42.08,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,It was just one time, \Nbut I had a really terrible thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.99,0:06:55.50,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,"What if he stays with me \Nand the two of them break up?"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.21,0:06:59.98,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,It was such a selfish thing to think.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.83,0:07:03.94,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,Mitsuki was...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.65,0:07:09.47,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,Mitsuki was depending on me for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.91,0:07:15.08,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,And even then, I... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.41,0:07:20.37,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so bad. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.14,0:07:23.81,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.21,0:07:39.43,Default,Koto,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much for your hospitality.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.43,0:07:41.64,Default,Lemon's Grandma,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all. It was my pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.35,0:07:45.55,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Nukumizu-kun. That T-shirt...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.55,0:07:49.13,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,That's mine, you know. \NI'm glad it fits you okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.13,0:07:51.70,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? This is your shirt, Yakishio?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.00,0:07:53.83,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,R-Really? I'll take it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.83,0:07:55.91,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,It's just an extra one I had. No big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.91,0:07:58.79,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,I tried to lend it to Yana-chan \Nyesterday, but it was too—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.79,0:07:59.87,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,Lemon-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.87,0:08:03.41,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,I told you not to tell anyone \Nabout that! Didn't I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.87,0:08:04.27,Top,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, who cares? It's just Nuk-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.41,0:08:07.04,Italics,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,So Yanami put this on and it didn't fit?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.27,0:08:05.61,Top,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I{\i0} care!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.06,0:08:09.39,Default,Koto,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like everything's working out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.89,0:08:12.17,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't do anything special.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.35,0:08:17.34,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,All we can really do is watch over her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.76,0:08:21.45,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,But, uh, could you please \Ngive me some space here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.45,0:08:26.73,Default,Koto,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Does me being this close make you \Nnervous? Aw, that makes me so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.44,0:08:31.24,Default,Komari,0000,0000,0000,,Sexual harassment.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.24,0:08:34.75,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Now, hold on! \NI'm the one getting harassed here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.84,0:08:39.77,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for coming, guys. \NI'll see you back at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.77,0:08:42.30,Default,Lemon's Grandma,0000,0000,0000,,Lemon really has some lovely friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.64,0:08:47.34,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think so? The girls in the \Nliterature club are a little eccentric.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.34,0:08:50.17,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,They're kind of fearless, \Nbut not necessarily in a good way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.17,0:08:54.63,Default,Lemon's Grandma,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, when I said that, Nukumizu-kun,\N I was thinking of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.78,0:08:58.51,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,Hey there, Nuk-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.12,0:09:02.06,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go talk to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.15,0:09:04.87,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,Mitsuki and Asagumo-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.72,0:09:17.36,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,Asagumo-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.07,0:09:20.81,Default,Chihaya,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time we've \Nbeen alone together, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.36,0:09:22.49,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.11,0:09:25.21,Default,Chihaya,0000,0000,0000,,Yakishio-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.44,0:09:31.06,Default,Chihaya,0000,0000,0000,,Would you mind if we talked a little? \NI would like to get to know you better.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.73,0:09:37.80,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,Mm-hmm. I would, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.82,0:09:49.81,Default,Chihaya,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, after you, Yakishio-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.81,0:09:51.57,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Asagumo-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.57,0:09:53.06,Default,Chihaya,0000,0000,0000,,You're very welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.62,0:09:55.65,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,Asagumo-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.65,0:09:57.68,Default,Chihaya,0000,0000,0000,,I'll join you in a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.65,0:09:58.86,Default,text,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\shad0\blur0.3\b1\an8\frx34\fs18\fax0.14\pos(55,118.5)}Other\N\hTrash
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.03,0:10:09.28,Default,Chihaya,0000,0000,0000,,I ended up breaking my promise just once.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.28,0:10:10.18,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.18,0:10:12.88,Default,Chihaya,0000,0000,0000,,But I think this really is the end of it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.70,0:10:16.84,Default,Chihaya,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't tell \NNukumizu-san about it, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.44,0:10:30.40,Default,text,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\b1\bord2.5\shad1.5\blur0.3\fs15\fscx90\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\pos(20,81.333)}The Most Popular Girl in Class
